Simple projects:
----------------
Face recognition
Text recognition
Number plate recognition
Person count in an image

Projects that might include video processing:
----------------------------------------
Background estimation in an image
Signature verification
Handwriting recognition- Identify whose handwriting this is
Movement recognition: Incoming and outgoing persons count in a video
Use case: Lets say we want to count the foot fall in a shop in a mall between particular timings in a day.


